        +++++++++++++++++
        
        * Implemented `validate_filename` handler in `TusCreateMixin`.
        
        1.15 (2017-04-06)
        +++++++++++++++++
        
        * Added missing migration and changed max_length to 255 for model `Upload`'s attribute `uploaded_file`
        
        1.14 (2017-03-30)
